M
n\times n
\|M\|_1 = \sum_{ij} |M_{ij}|
\|M\|_1 
|\det M|
m = \operatorname{max}_{ij} |M_{ij}|
|\det M| \leq \sum_{\sigma \in S_n} m^n = n! m^n \quad  or \quad  \|M\|_1  \geq m \geq (|\det M|/n!)^{\frac1n}.
v_1,\ldots,v_n
M
|\det M|\leq \prod_{j=1}^n\lVert v_j\rVert_2
\lVert v_j\rVert_2^2 =\left(\sum_{k=1}^n|m_{kj}|\right)^2-2\sum_{j<k}|m_{jk}|\leq \left(\sum_{k=1}^n|m_{kj}|\right)^2
\lVert v_j\rVert_2\leq \sum_{k=1}^n|m_{jk}|\leq \lVert M\rVert_1
|\det M|^{\frac 1n}\leq \lVert M\rVert_1
